URL - Uniform Resource Locator
ğŸ“Œ URL FORMAT :
          schema://domain:port/query_string#fragment_id
Example : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org


ğŸ“Œ Several parts of URL : 
âœ”ï¸ Schema or Protocol - http,https,ftp.....
âœ”ï¸ Sever domain name - .edu , .com , .org ,....
âœ”ï¸ Port(default : 80) - Optional
âœ”ï¸ Path to resource with name & extension - .html....
